      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's the thing though, the friends and family stuff feels like a script. Most people only care if I hit my deadlines or if I reply to a text. If I just... wasn't there anymore. If I just stopped showing up to the calls or stopped responding to everything entirely. Would anyone actually even notice if I just disappeared? Like, if I just faded out?",
